data.description: Welcome to your Beach Retreat. Relax on the front porch. Enjoy the Yachts going by on the Intercostal. With a painted Indian Sunset View. Home is within walking distance to your own beach access. This home has a back porch with Ocean breeze's and the sound of waves for your Relaxation. Also has a beautiful view of a the Golf Course. This home comes with Hurricane Shutters and partial outdoor furniture included. Home has brand new Roof 2023. Home just got a Beautiful New Paint/Trim on outside of a Beachy Color. This home also comes with Gorgeous Landscape and Sprinkler Irrigation System. All upgrades inside home. Where done in 2019. The inside of home is just breathtaking. As you walk in this home you get a Tommy Bahama Decor feel. Partial Furniture included. This home has beautiful inside shutters and 2 living areas along with huge kitchen, Dining area and Gorgeous large bedrooms. Master bath has a Jacuzzi/Shower combo with heat lamps in bathrooms. There is also a huge sunroom that is decorated with beach colors. Which can also be used as playroom. 3rd bathroom is out in garage. To rinse off those Sandy toes from the beach. The driveway is big enough for a Boat or RV. Very Beautiful neighborhood with No HOA. Bring your toys. Marina, fishing and Pier close by. This home has so much to offer. Beach Access.
